trans-unit.source: A unique title for you to identify the Documents Import with
Reference to the Documents Import Export file
Last processed file hash, used solely by the importer. Don't change this value unless you know what you're doing.

When enabled, will allow the import to only retain data from the very latest update it received. This is useful for use-cases where the import-updates provided represent the total amount of Decos DMS data to be usable by the extension for this specific import.
